@KorID.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5222

GET {{KorID.API_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

### Rejestracja nowego użytkownika
POST {{KorID.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nowy_uzytkownik",
  "email": "nowy@example.com",
  "password": "SuperTajneHaslo123!"
}

### Logowanie (sprawdzenie czy działa)
POST {{KorID.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nowy_uzytkownik",
  "password": "SuperTajneHaslo123!"
}
### Logowanie (sprawdzenie czy działa admin)
POST {{KorID.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nowy_uzytkownik",
  "password": "SuperTajneHaslo123!"
}

### External login - ping (sanity)
GET http://localhost:5222/api/external/ping
Accept: application/json

### List applications (to verify seeded demo app)
GET http://localhost:5222/api/applications
Accept: application/json

### List users (verify seeded demo user)
GET http://localhost:5222/api/users
Accept: application/json

### Check user-application grants
GET http://localhost:5222/api/userapplications
Accept: application/json

### External login (simulate external app calling KorID)
POST http://localhost:5222/api/external/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "changeme",
  "applicationId": 1,
  "redirectUrl": "http://localhost:5173/test/callback"
}

### External login - wrong password example
POST http://localhost:5222/api/external/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "wrong",
  "applicationId": 200,
  "redirectUrl": "http://localhost:5173/test/callback"
}

### External login - missing grant (use another user or app id)
POST http://localhost:5222/api/external/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "changeme",
  "applicationId": 9999,
  "redirectUrl": "http://localhost:5173/test/callback"
}
